Class ObjectDBClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.webservicecore.network.WebServiceClient
      • fr.webservicecore.junit.network.ObjectDBClient
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ObjectDBTokenClient

    public class ObjectDBClient
extends WebServiceClient
    Example of WebService client to test NodeJS module named 'WebServiceCore'

    This class uses directly HttpRequest class by its extension of the WebService class The protected functions are used as auxiliary functions to be reused by an extension of it
